    <section name="Introduction">
        <subsection name="What is the properties component?">
            <p>
              The properties component allows you to create simple CMS documents 
              having a flat list of name/value pairs. It also provides easy locating 
              and using these documents in your HST site frontend.
            </p>
        </subsection>
